name: NFTime
description:
There is no single timezone for NFTs.  Instead, NFTime is the shared experience of living and breathing inside the NFT space.  Here, time moves 2x as fast.
Side effects of this experience includes FUD, FOMO, a buildup of deadlines, and a chance of NGMI.

This clock has been designed specifically for NFT space and adjusted to tick at every second of NFTime.
